languages.text: "Все путешествия госпожи Теодоры можно было назвать необычными. Она была дерзка в своих экспедициях. Что до этих слов... на первый взгляд, ничего такого не припомню".
"All of Lady Theodora's journeys could be considered unusual. Her odysseys were always audacious. As for the words you mentioned... None of them sounds familiar to me as far as I can tell."

languages.text: « Tous les voyages de dame Théodora étaient inhabituels, d'une certaine façon. Chacune de ses entreprises était audacieuse. Quant aux termes dont vous parlez, aucun ne m'évoque quoi que ce soit. »
languages.original_text: "All of Lady Theodora's journeys could be considered unusual. Her odysseys were always audacious. As for the words you mentioned... None of them sounds familiar to me as far as I can tell."

traits.locale_text: « Tous les voyages de dame Théodora étaient inhabituels, d'une certaine façon. Ils repoussaient toujours les limites. Quant aux termes dont vous parlez, aucun ne m'évoque quoi que ce soit. »

languages.text: “西奥多拉夫人的所有旅行都不同寻常，她每场冒险都相当敢作敢为。至于您提到的这些词……我并没有什么特别的印象。”
languages.original_text: "All of Lady Theodora's journeys could be considered unusual. Her odysseys were always audacious. As for the words you mentioned... None of them sounds familiar to me as far as I can tell."

traits.locale_text: “西奥多拉夫人的所有旅行都不同寻常，她每场冒险都是在挑战极限。至于您提到的这些词……我并没有什么特别的印象。”

languages.text: "Lady Theodoras Reisen können samt und sonders als ungewöhnlich angesehen werden. Ihre Odysseen waren immer kühn. Und was die erwähnten Worte angeht ... Keines davon kommt mir bekannt vor, so weit ich das sagen kann."
languages.original_text: "All of Lady Theodora's journeys could be considered unusual. Her odysseys were always audacious. As for the words you mentioned... None of them sounds familiar to me as far as I can tell."

traits.locale_text: "Lady Theodoras Reisen können samt und sonders als ungewöhnlich angesehen werden. Ihre Odysseen haben Grenzen verschoben. Und was die erwähnten Worte angeht ... Keines davon kommt mir bekannt vor, so weit ich das sagen kann."

languages.text: «Todos los viajes de Theodora eran inusuales. Siempre estaba desafiando límites. En cuanto a las palabras que ha mencionado... Ninguna me resulta familiar, por lo menos a primera vista».
languages.original_text: "All of Lady Theodora's journeys could be considered unusual. Her odysseys were always audacious. As for the words you mentioned... None of them sounds familiar to me as far as I can tell."

traits.locale_text: «Todos los viajes de Theodora eran verdaderamente inusuales. Siempre estaba desafiando límites. En cuanto a las palabras que ha mencionado... Ninguna me resulta familiar según lo que sé».

languages.text: 「シオドーラ様の旅は、そのどれもが一風変わっていたと言っても過言ではないでしょう。彼女の冒険はすべて大胆でした。そして、あなたの仰られた言葉については…私の知る限り、どれも聞き覚えがありません」
languages.original_text: "All of Lady Theodora's journeys could be considered unusual. Her odysseys were always audacious. As for the words you mentioned... None of them sounds familiar to me as far as I can tell."

languages.text: "Leydi Theodora'nın tüm seyahatleri olağan dışı olarak değerlendirilebilir. Her zaman gözü pek maceralara atılırdı. Sözünü ettiğiniz kavramlar ise... Bana hiçbiri tanıdık gelmiyor doğrusu."
